text: Rodriguez's Amazon tree frog, Senaris' tree frog, Kaieteur Tepui tree frog, or Gorzula's Amazon tree frog (Tepuihyla rodriguezi) is a frog. It lives in Venezuela and Guyana. Scientists have seen it between 366 and 2440 meters above sea level. ==References== Category:Frogs of South America
title: Tepuihyla rodriguezi
